    "description": "WelcomHeritage Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Guest Relations Manager at our Mysuru location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout WelcomHeritage Holdings Services:\nWelcomHeritage Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with WelcomHeritage Holdings Services!",
